TI  - Upturn in secondary forest clearing buffers primary forest loss in the Brazilian Amazon
T2  - NATURE SUSTAINABILITY
KW  - LAND-COVER
KW  - BIODIVERSITY
KW  - ACCURACY
KW  - STATE
