TI  - Arrested development? Investigating the role of bamboo in Araucaria Forest succession in Southern Brazil
T2  - JOURNAL OF PLANT ECOLOGY
KW  - dominant species
KW  - Merostachys skvortzovii Send.
KW  - forest succession
KW  - biodiversity
KW  - forest regeneration
