TI  - ESTIMATION OF BIOMASS CARBON STOCKS OVER PEAT SWAMP FORESTS USING MULTI-TEMPORAL AND MULTI-POLARIZATIONS SAR DATA
T2  - 36TH INTERNATIONAL SYMPOSIUM ON REMOTE SENSING OF ENVIRONMENT
KW  - forest carbon biomass
